        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName>
                            William Plomer writes to thank Mrs. Smallwood for sending him two copies of Sado. Plomer also mentions that John Morris of the BBC is interested in discussing the book in his overseas broadcasts and suggests that Morris be sent a review copy. Morris' private address is included in the letter.
                        </placeName>
                        <date when="YYYY-MM-DD">
                            13 June .51
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>
                            <persName key="Q7050230">Mrs. Smallwood</persName> 
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            29 Linden Gardens
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>W2
                        </addrLine>
                    </address>
                    <salute>
                       Dear Mrs Smallwood,
                    </salute>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    Thank you for<lb/>
                your letter &amp; for<lb/>
                so kindly sending me<lb/>
                two copies of <title>Sado</title>.<lb/>
                I am looking forward<lb/>
                to their arrival.<lb/>
                    <persName key="Q6249481">John Morris</persName>, head<lb/>
                of the Eastern dept<lb/>
                in the <orgName key="Q9531">B.B.C.</orgName>, would<lb/>
                like in due course to<pb/>
                talk about the book<lb/> 
                in his overseas<lb/>  
                broadcasts, so perhaps<lb/> 
                you might think it<lb/> 
                worthwhile to send<lb/> 
                him a review copy.<lb/> 
                His private address<lb/>  
                is <address>
                    <addrLine><emph rend="underlined">46 Hornton Court,</emph></addrLine>
                    <addrLine><emph rend="underlined">W.8.</emph></addrLine>
                </address><lb/> 
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>
                        Yours sincerely
                    </salute>
                    <signed/>
                    <seg type="postscript"> 
                        BBC European<lb/>
                        BBC Home<lb/>
                        have each been<lb/>
                        sent a review copy<lb/>
                        <unclear reason="bad handwriting" cert="low">Ml.</unclear> <date when="1951-06-13">13.6.51</date>
                    </seg>
